@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #146C94

title Authentication & Registration Flow

actor Student as S
participant "React\nRegister Page" as REG
participant "React\nLogin Page" as LOG
participant "API Client" as API
participant "Auth Views" as AUTH
participant "Email\nService" as EMAIL
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Registration ==

S -> REG : Fill form\n(name, email, password, role)
REG -> API : POST /api/auth/register/
API -> AUTH : CreateUser
AUTH -> DB : Insert User\n(is_verified=False)
AUTH -> AUTH : Generate 6-digit OTP
AUTH -> DB : Save OTP + timestamp
AUTH -> EMAIL : Send verification email\n(Gmail SMTP)
EMAIL --> S : OTP code via email
AUTH --> API : 201 (Check your email)
API --> REG : Show verify page

S -> REG : Enter OTP code
REG -> API : POST /api/auth/verify-email/
API -> AUTH : VerifyOTP
AUTH -> DB : Check OTP matches\n& not expired (10 min)
AUTH -> DB : Set is_verified=True
AUTH --> API : 200 (Email verified)
API --> REG : Redirect to login

== Login ==

S -> LOG : Enter email + password
LOG -> API : POST /api/token/
API -> AUTH : TokenObtainPair
AUTH -> DB : Validate credentials\n+ check is_verified
AUTH --> API : {access_token, refresh_token}
API -> API : Store tokens\nin localStorage
API --> LOG : Redirect to dashboard

== Token Refresh ==

API -> API : Access token expired?
API -> AUTH : POST /api/token/refresh/\n(refresh_token)
AUTH --> API : New access_token
note right : Automatic silent refresh\nbefore token expires

@enduml
